informed me of an
important new appointment

74
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:13,439
at Canterbury Cathedral.
Indeed.

75
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:15,999
Dr. Simon Heyes
has been made
our new dean.

76
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:18,279
Dr. Heyes detests
the cult of images

77
00:06:18,280 --> 00:06:20,959
and is determined
to remove them
from the cathedral,

78
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:22,999
as well as introducing
the new learning.

79
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:26,439
It is vital that we place reformers
in positions of responsibility

80
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:28,119
inside the church.

81
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:31,119
There's bound to be a reaction
to the self-serving martyrdoms

82
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,679
of Fisher and More.

83
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:35,919
Which is why I'm letting it
be known that if anyone
hears a friend

84
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:39,919
or a neighbour criticising
the king or his marriage
or the reforms,

85
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:42,519
they have a duty to report it.

86
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:47,959
At the same time, Mr. Cromwell,
we have a duty to spread
the good news.

87
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:51,599
If the new monarchy is about
anything at all, it is about liberty.

88
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:55,119
Liberty from old superstitions,
from fear and guilt.

89
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:58,519
We-- We are moving, my friends,
from the darkness into the light.

90
00:06:58,520 --> 00:07:01,479
I'm in agreement with Your Grace.

91
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:04,550
Fortunately,
we have a new weapon

92
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:07,199
to promote our ideas.

93
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:22,159
CRANMER:
Oh, my Lord.

94
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:24,720
What in God's name is that?

95
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:31,770
It's called a printing press, My Lord.

96
00:07:32,400 --> 00:07:34,900
Beautiful.

97
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:37,750
And it will change the world.

98
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:50,100
What are you thinking of?

99
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:53,820
Nothing.

100
00:08:02,280 --> 00:08:04,780
May I say something?

101
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:07,599
You know there are
many people abroad,

102
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:10,759
and perhaps even some
within this kingdom,

103
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:15,290
who still question
the legitimacy of our daughter.

104
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:18,210
It's true. You know it's true.

105
00:08:20,640 --> 00:08:25,079
But there is something we can do
to change everything.

106
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:26,679
If Elizabeth was betrothed

107
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:30,799
to King Francis' youngest son,
the duke of Angoulême,

108
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:32,599
then her legitimacy and station

109
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:36,280
would no longer be questioned
by anyone.

110
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:38,239
I agree.

111
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:41,239
And have already thought about it.

112
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:44,760
I will speak
to the French ambassador.

113
00:08:47,640 --> 00:08:50,140
[SlGHS]

114
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:54,160
Will you come to my bed tonight?

115
00:09:10,040 --> 00:09:11,599
HENRY:
Dear Thomas.

116
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:13,479
Majesty.

117
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:15,039
Come stay at court.
I need you.

118
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:16,519
HENRY:
I'm not going to sign it.

119
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:18,839
You want the world to know
the king is changeable?

120
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,759
--whether it is better
for a king to be feared--

121
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:22,519
I don't want to be chancellor.
--or loved.

122
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:24,159
You will do as I command.

123
00:09:24,160 --> 00:09:26,660
[###]

124
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:27,959
Harry. Harry.

125
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,519
I come to offer my resignation.

126
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:30,999
The time for Harry is over.

127
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:33,879
HENRY:
I discharge you. Most willingly.

128
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:38,599
COMMlSSlONER: --your head cut off,
your body to be divided in four parts.

129
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:40,519
