144
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:04,620
No.

145
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:09,199
You are marrying
into a great family.

146
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:14,940
You will do it whether
you like it or not.
Do you understand?

147
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:34,540
[SPEAKlNG lN LATlN

148
