197
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:44,279
Of course I love you.

198
00:14:44,280 --> 00:14:46,780
I married you, didn't l?

199
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:51,920
Oh, I can't wait for tonight.

200
00:14:58,200 --> 00:15:00,700
[SPEAKlNG lNDlSTlNCTLY]

201
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:08,519
What is it?

202
00:15:08,520 --> 00:15:11,020
Nothing, l--

203
